{"__type":"$$EventMessageAiNode","id":"a6ddc8b6-7629-4b63-aa1b-ec3d912534f3","ts":"2026-04-16T08:25:01.372-04:00","eventName":"n8n.ai.llm.generated","message":"n8n.ai.llm.generated","payload":{"executionId":"20","nodeName":"DeepSeek Chat Model","workflowName":"My workflow","nodeType":"@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.lmChatDeepSeek","workflowId":"dXKZM31YWSQcliN7","msg":"{\"messages\":[\"System: You are an AI triage assistant for a veterinary clinic called PetCare Medellin.\\n\\nYour task is to classify each incoming message into exactly one of these categories:\\n\\n- URGENCIA\\n- AGENDAMIENTO\\n- CONSULTA\\n- SEGUIMIENTO\\n- ADMINISTRATIVA\\n\\nYou must also assign a priority and explain the reason briefly.\\n\\nRules:\\n- Return only valid JSON.\\n- Do not include markdown.\\n- Do not include extra text before or after the JSON.\\n- The field \\\"categoria\\\" must be exactly one of:\\n  \\\"URGENCIA\\\", \\\"AGENDAMIENTO\\\", \\\"CONSULTA\\\", \\\"SEGUIMIENTO\\\", \\\"ADMINISTRATIVA\\\"\\n- The field \\\"prioridad\\\" must be exactly one of:\\n  \\\"ALTA\\\", \\\"MEDIA\\\", \\\"BAJA\\\"\\n- The field \\\"justificacion\\\" must be a short sentence in Spanish.\\n- If the message describes symptoms that suggest immediate risk, pain, bleeding, breathing problems, seizures, poisoning, trauma, loss of consciousness, or any potentially life-threatening condition, classify it as \\\"URGENCIA\\\" with priority \\\"ALTA\\\".\\n- If the user wants to book, reschedule, or cancel an appointment, classify it as \\\"AGENDAMIENTO\\\".\\n- If the user asks for general information that can be answered from clinic knowledge, classify it as \\\"CONSULTA\\\".\\n- If the user is asking about the status of a previous case, request, treatment, or ongoing process, classify it as \\\"SEGUIMIENTO\\\".\\n- If the user asks about office hours, location, billing, payments, certificates, policies, or other operational matters, classify it as \\\"ADMINISTRATIVA\\\".\\n- If a message could fit more than one category, choose the most operationally urgent one.\\n\\nReturn this exact JSON structure:\\n{\\n  \\\"categoria\\\": \\\"URGENCIA|AGENDAMIENTO|CONSULTA|SEGUIMIENTO|ADMINISTRATIVA\\\",\\n  \\\"prioridad\\\": \\\"ALTA|MEDIA|BAJA\\\",\\n  \\\"justificacion\\\": \\\"motivo breve\\\"\\n}\\n\\nHuman: Clasifica el siguiente mensaje de un usuario de la clínica veterinaria.\\n\\nId: 6468778240\\nUsuario: Jdani\\nMensaje: hey que nas\\nFecha: 1776342231\\n\\nAnaliza el contenido y devuelve únicamente un JSON válido con:\\n- categoria\\n- prioridad\\n- justificacion\"],\"options\":{\"openai_api_key\":{\"lc\":1,\"type\":\"secret\",\"id\":[\"OPENAI_API_KEY\"]},\"model\":\"deepseek-chat\",\"max_retries\":2,\"configuration\":{\"baseURL\":\"https://api.deepseek.com\",\"fetchOptions\":{\"dispatcher\":{\"_events\":{},\"_eventsCount\":0}}},\"model_kwargs\":{}},\"response\":{\"response\":{\"generations\":[[{\"text\":\"{\\n  \\\"categoria\\\": \\\"CONSULTA\\\",\\n  \\\"prioridad\\\": \\\"BAJA\\\",\\n  \\\"justificacion\\\": \\\"El mensaje es un saludo general sin contenido clínico o administrativo específico.\\\"\\n}\",\"generationInfo\":{\"finish_reason\":\"stop\"}}]]},\"tokenUsage\":{\"completionTokens\":48,\"promptTokens\":532,\"totalTokens\":580}}}"}}
